[0m[49m[39m  321, 313[0m:[39m[49m ## Step 4: Record the Verification Attempt
[0m[49m[39m  322, 314[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 323     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m *Every verification attempt gets an audit record. This is non-negotiable in healthcare. You need to know who was verified, when, whether it succeeded, and what the confidence was. This feeds compliance reporting and fraud investigation.*
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      315[0m:[38;5;10m[49m *The pseudocode calls this `log_verification`. Every verification attempt gets an audit record. This is non-negotiable in healthcare. You need to know who was verified, when, whether it succeeded, and what the confidence was. This feeds compliance reporting and fraud investigation.*
[0m[49m[39m  324, 316[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  325, 317[0m:[39m[49m ```python
[0m[49m[39m  326, 318[0m:[39m[49m def record_verification_attempt(
